                    <persName corresp="#p_HHL1">Hopkins</persName> Papers</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Sketch by <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> To
                        Illustrate His Concept of the United Nations Organization</hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d394fn1">The words in the upper right corner
                        “T[ehran]-misc[ellanous]” were added subsequently as a file indicator. The
                        writing enclosed in the circles reads: “40 U. N.”, “Exec[utive]
                        Com[mittee]”, and “4 Police [men]”. The words below the left-hand circle are
                        “I[nternational] L[abor] O[rganization]-Health Agric[ulture]-Food”.</note>
                </head>
